{"tid":893912,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"進擊的巨人 111 森林出身的孩童 英文","createTime":"2018-11-08T04:03:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-09T16:21:25.000Z","uid":198822,"like":15,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"338ca5b8d05ff5b934a3851f0e7cb7d34b390e1d","tid":893912,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T04:03:31.000Z","msg":"連登仔英文程度睇得明啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://imgur.com/a/mv9mAN3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2Fa%2Fmv9mAN3&d=AM57Ty9dh6zc9ptDLz4hr%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=a41d0c30\" target=\"_blank\">https://imgur.com/a/mv9mAN3</a><br />\n<br />\n希望大家尊重並鼓勵番呢班無償翻譯嘅同好<br />\n唔好見遲少少就屌<br />\nBeggars are not choosers<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdb4d6021201acbd29d46d8a716b55f47f0f03de","tid":893912,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T04:07:19.000Z","msg":"皮克西斯都幾醒目<br />\n因為知道在場仲有艾撚fans<br />\n所以無屌過艾倫 費事畀人炸死之餘<br />\n又可以組織到班人制衡艾撚<br />\n<br />\nbtw 黑人有鬼啦 睇佢同廚師講野個Tone都知<br />\n<br />\n同埋兵長都幾危險 得30人加上唔知政局丕變 會唔會死於內戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b292f0531ca50ae9532074e0a1c6f278c0187c4","tid":893912,"uid":198822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T04:11:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tieba.baidu.com/p/5940838768?pn=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftieba.baidu.com%2Fp%2F5940838768%3Fpn%3D1&d=AM57Ty9dh6zc9ptDLz4hr%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=fa6a081e\" target=\"_blank\">https://tieba.baidu.com/p/5940838768?pn=1</a><br />\n後半段嘅中文版"},{"pid":"5fd2ace26561f20f796e973fa957bf9e73ad275e","tid":893912,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T04:59:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"014b7bbb6537c94a1afddbb7df40dd262a12e118","tid":893912,"uid":198822,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T05:17:17.000Z","msg":"今集莎夏老豆都講得幾好<br />\n<br />\n莎夏一直都係獵人，只係獵嘅由畜牲變成敵人，為嘅由美食變成生存。<br />\n殺與被殺，又豈止於原始嘅生物鏈？天下本身，正是血肉橫飛嘅一片叢林。相殘而死，正是森林中屢見不鮮嘅景象。<br />\n<br />\n莎夏老豆話要和平，就要離開森林。只係以世界之大，卻似無林外之地，實在可笑可嘆。"},{"pid":"b0cd9598f04d77e52929e52a642b4c9942aecc31","tid":893912,"uid":120852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T05:37:32.000Z","msg":"D酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 班軍人全部中哂伏"},{"pid":"bec7410ab073aa1a4672ccd0adac9142a08bf4a5","tid":893912,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0cd9598f04d77e52929e52a642b4c9942aecc31","tid":893912,"uid":120852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T05:37:32.000Z","msg":"D酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 班軍人全部中哂伏"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T05:43:39.000Z","msg":"應該有啲人冇飲<br />\n例如憲兵團團長奈爾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed5b908f57068fa4ef15683f64667d16a7b39223","tid":893912,"uid":121546,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T07:40:56.000Z","msg":"sasha D朋友入面得尼哥洛可以諗都唔諗就郁手殺加bitch"},{"pid":"6c01147379b2f70ed5b547ee39caae2f97ee63dd","tid":893912,"uid":82344,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"014b7bbb6537c94a1afddbb7df40dd262a12e118","tid":893912,"uid":198822,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T05:17:17.000Z","msg":"今集莎夏老豆都講得幾好<br />\n<br />\n莎夏一直都係獵人，只係獵嘅由畜牲變成敵人，為嘅由美食變成生存。<br />\n殺與被殺，又豈止於原始嘅生物鏈？天下本身，正是血肉橫飛嘅一片叢林。相殘而死，正是森林中屢見不鮮嘅景象。<br />\n<br />\n莎夏老豆話要和平，就要離開森林。只係以世界之大，卻似無林外之地，實在可笑可嘆。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T08:24:20.000Z","msg":"第一代王就嘗試離開森林建造樂園，但係..."},{"pid":"a7