n而係有冇外人可以見證兩族和平共處，再生存落去傳揚所見所聞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T09:32:49.000Z","msg":"然後呢?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T09:41:12.000Z","msg":"當輿論已成，咁各國政府就會有制肘，唔會咁易聯合攻島<br />\n<br />\n呢個就係阿爾敏嘅計劃。但係艾倫嘅行動令各國人難以訪島，東洋人利字當頭唔會幫手，理論上受感化嘅義勇兵又暗受吉克指使。所以呢個計劃呢家行唔通。<br />\n<br />\n可行嘅方法係世界攻島，艾倫用地鳴不戰而屈人，阿爾敏為首嘅鴿派禮待戰俘，吉克/萊納行出嚟將矛頭指向前東家馬萊。咁樣島可保全，聲名可善，並可向馬萊報仇。<br />\n<br />\n但係最大問題係吉克有自己嘅agenda，萊納心繫馬萊家人。馬加特嘅取態應為關鍵。"},{"pid":"a2a094cc40f3a4cc33c2fac2d1d164ee52f0c099","tid":893912,"uid":173852,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T10:04:26.000Z","msg":"睇下依集又要幫諫山吹奏多次 真係痴撚線  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ea619fafd42acd3dad6b3f711a9c9636ab9a077","tid":893912,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2a094cc40f3a4cc33c2fac2d1d164ee52f0c099","tid":893912,"uid":173852,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T10:04:26.000Z","msg":"睇下依集又要幫諫山吹奏多次 真係痴撚線  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T10:12:10.000Z","msg":"莎夏老豆個part已經超哂班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32b5919c4c1fa081f3c8914849af70deb36c57d0","tid":893912,"uid":45525,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a2a094cc40f3a4cc33c2fac2d1d164ee52f0c099","tid":893912